twitch_info.title: I wanna kill the kamilia 3 v2.02 - The Journey to 100% (Beaten K3 v1.50 100%)

message.body: I could beat this any day at this point
taking me a while to get used to the tas drop again
I typically do badly before a good rn anyway
best time to say gl is when I actually grab the crystal
it's common for me to get to the middle now
it's grabbing the crystal that's rare
when I grab the crystal is the real moment to give gl since it's all to play at that point
what makes this level so dangerous tbh is just
the so many near perfect inputs
and then the perfect inputs required for the supper fs on top of that
there's two sets of perfect inputs you can attempt for the middle section
as far as I saw in jtool so it's like pick your poison lol
one of them you can doa jump cancel setup to give a bit more of a window on 2nd jump variability but the timing becomes much worse
chances of clearing ex air crystal are super, super low
even if you're really good the chances of you lining up all of the required inputs is just tiny
I imagine the people cracked at needle would prove me wrong ofc
this crystal is genuinely unreasonable imo
I do not think I could've done tis crystal back during my v1.50 100% grind
fortunately this crystal didn't exist back then :)
pluto is right tho this probably is harder than guy tower crystal lol
good progress so far in 22 minutes
approaching my usual progress rn lol
and this is why I hate super fs
you either get them first try or after a long tme or not at all
one of the most unreliable fangame jumps
in my 4 hour session yesterday I only grabbed the crystal twice iirc
probably will be the same today
At first, that crystal path doesn't even look too bad. Really deceptive jumps, lol
it's the hardest part of the screen
no other jump compares to it on this screen
those last two middle jumps are diabolical to put this far into a save
because it's so hard you're likely gonna only get past it once or twice per session
and even if you do manage it, there's the backtrack and the super fs after
this crystal is not designed to be beaten imo
it's a giant "fuck you" to anyone going for 100% LUL
we die on that one LUL
the 1st hardest is in ex m-stage
I'm over 21 hours into trying to get this EX Air crystal
for context, EX Air originally took me 21 hours to clear
so this is harder than clearing it normally by a good margin lol
heyo gl with ex air crystal
i beat that hard save I've been posting about
I'm not aware of it, but gj!
will be a cool video from you thenthough :D
I still hate super fs lmao
I either get them first try or it takes ages or not at all
At least you can try these ones again if you fall
it's still very easy to walk back into the spike instead
or jump into the spike cause you jumped too low
or fail to jump on the same frame and walk instead
the frame counter? oh it's aurora's input viewer
I got it from iwannacommunity forum iirc
I have yet to grab the crystal this session, but I did grab it twice last session
hopefully in the next 3 hours I can get it once lol
that is the kind of time scale we're looking at unfortunately
yee v1.50 was a while ago now, I keep it in the stream title so everyone knows that this playthrough is just doing 100% clean up on v2.00+
Oh, ok, because I remember Emperor EX very recently
yeah my ex emperor clear was when I got v1.50 100% yeee
ex emperor was my final content left you see xD
then I copied my save over to v2.00+
and have since been finishing the 100% on v2.00+
it's gtonna take ages though lol
once I get EX Air Crystal, I've got golden 3 and golden 4 to do
then I got ouka area, tomo area and then finally ex m-stage
so like there isn't much content to do left
the problem is just how hard and long the rest is
Indeed, epic grinds, but I believe
over 21 hours in this ex air crystal already, it's insanely hard LUL
i also broke 1000 hours in-game time
if we count practice tool it's more but ye
glad this game's timer can even count that far lol
I don't really think about my death count at this point lol
time and deaths have lost all meaning now
except time spent on individual stuff, that still matters - but as a whole
depending how close I get to it after 100% it might be worth playing the game after to reach it
that was my first time getting the crystal this session, hopefully we can get another lmao
at least I've had two deaths at the super fs with the crystal now
I do the super f first to trigger the trap so I don't have to deal with the trap after the crystal
I've only reached the super fs with the crystal twice ever so far
mfw now I'm mis-timing the second jump input on the two diagonals lol
dang so close to grabbing the crystal oof
I didn;t see, please do it again :)
but I can't guarantee when I will make it lol
oooo this is the super F save xdd
the crystal is horrible to get
and the super fs make it all worse lmao
there is where you are wrong
Super F is the cherry of the cake
this without super F is like a cake without cherry
I'd take the cake without cherry any day lol
what is wrong on that jump?
the problem is it's a double diagonal
the timing of the double jump is extremely precise
guess you could try it in maker then?
if it comes to it I'll switch to linux lmao
Santa: ask me whatever for christmass. ME:I Want a car. Santa: I can't give you that. ME: Then make eradem clear this screen. Santa: What color would you like the car to be? humzhShiver
haven't heard that meme in a hot minute
ok fight me to dead, no shirt
but that's my 3rd time making it to super fs with crystal iirc
but dont die to the super f please
I had one attempt reach the final super f once
super fs are a LOT harder than you thnk LUL
triple frame perfects are such a pain tho
ye true but you only gotta do one
so you can try a lot
that is true but you also can jump too low and not manage that
since the jump height you need to get across is always the same and if you shoot above it you always miss
and if you shoot below it you die
worse is if you're too close to the spike then you gotta jump on the same frame
hold a number and then press arrow
or are you not usinh notepad?
the setup for doing super fs with numpad can be done but it's harder to learn
then we only have one option
this is because you can't bonk
yeah if you bnonk you dont reach
they call them super F because they are super FUCKED
as you can see here problem is if you numpad it, pressing the arrow even slightly means full jump
I've been told by lovey01 there is a way to mitigate this but it's hard to learn lmao
so essentially yes I need to somehow be be perfect twice at the end after crystal
there is at least a silver-lining tbf
I would've beat this save already if not for crystal xD
and you saw how stupid the middle is to get crystal now LUL
prolly won't beat this tonight ngl
I have to do every stream expecting not to win at this point lmao
ye I think imma call it here tonight. Tomorrow though, we'll see.
